2025-06-13 22:03:39.166 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:03:39.188 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:04:39.463 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:04:39.466 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:05:39.604 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:06:39.727 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:07:39.843 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:08:39.986 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:09:40.103 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:10:40.212 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:11:40.350 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:12:40.469 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:13:40.604 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:14:40.715 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:15:40.827 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:16:40.949 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:17:41.080 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:18:41.189 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:18:41.192 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:19:41.309 [Information] Spovest.Infrastructure.Services.PriceUpdateService: Начало обновления цен
2025-06-13 22:19:41.313 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:19:41.316 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:20:41.444 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:20:41.446 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:20:41.447 [Information] Spovest.Infrastructure.Services.PriceUpdateService: Получены текущие цены для 30 игроков
2025-06-13 22:20:41.448 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Prices" AS p

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:21:41.579 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

FROM "Prices" AS p

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:22:41.688 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:23:41.808 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:24:41.930 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"

2025-06-13 22:25:42.100 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:26:29.744 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

2025-06-13 22:26:29.766 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:27:30.034 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:27:30.036 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:28:30.204 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:29:30.342 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:30:30.482 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:31:30.637 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:32:32.031 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

2025-06-13 22:32:32.052 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:33:23.894 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:33:23.914 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:34:24.200 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p
GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
2025-06-13 22:34:24.207 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

SELECT p."PlayerId", count(*)::int AS "Count"
FROM "Prices" AS p

2025-06-13 22:35:24.519 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"

2025-06-13 22:35:34.463 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."PlayerId", p3."PurchasePrice", p3."SalePrice", p3.c
FROM (
    SELECT p."PlayerId"
    FROM "Prices" AS p
    GROUP BY p."PlayerId"
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."PurchasePrice", p2."SalePrice", p2.c, p2."PlayerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p0."Purchase_price", 0.0) AS "PurchasePrice", COALESCE(p0."Sale_price", 0.0) AS "SalePrice", 1 AS c, p0."PlayerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY p0."PlayerId" ORDER BY p0."Timestamp" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Prices" AS p0
    ) AS p2
    WHERE p2.row <= 1
) AS p3 ON p1."PlayerId" = p3."PlayerId"
